{"title": "Edge of the Knife", "description": "The Terro-Human Future History is Piper's detailed account of the next 6000 years of human history. 1942, the year the first fission reactor was constructed, is defined as the year 1 A.E. (Atomic Era). In 1973, a nuclear war devastates the planet, eventually laying the groundwork for the emergence of a Terran Federation, once humanity goes into space and develops antigravity technology.<br /><br />\n\nThe story \"The Edge of the Knife\" (collected in Empire) occurs slightly before the war, and involves a man who sees flashes of the future. It links many key elements of Piper's series. (Summary from Wikipedia)", "duration": 6502, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "1560", "name": "H. Beam Piper"}], "coverArt": "https://www.archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt15/Edge_Knife_1203.jpg", "copyright_year": "1957", "genres": ["Science Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "jfmarchini"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "jfmarchini"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Karen Savage"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "dusty"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Part 01", "readers": [3144], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/edge_of_the_knife_0902_librivox/theedgeoftheknife_01_hbeampiper_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1137}, {"section": 2, "title": "Part 02", "readers": [3144], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/edge_of_the_knife_0902_librivox/theedgeoftheknife_02_hbeampiper_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1107}, {"section": 3, "title": "Part 03", "readers": [3144], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/edge_of_the_knife_0902_librivox/theedgeoftheknife_03_hbeampiper_64kb.mp3", "duration": 904}, {"section": 4, "title": "Part 04", "readers": [3144], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/edge_of_the_knife_0902_librivox/theedgeoftheknife_04_hbeampiper_64kb.mp3", "duration": 960}, {"section": 5, "title": "Part 05", "readers": [3144], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/edge_of_the_knif